OL,6,FAuthor Pat Barker, known for The
OL,7,FRegeneration Trilogy, thought the
OL,8,Fletter announcing her damehood in the
OL,9,FKing's Birthday Honours was an income
OL,10,Ftax bill and that HMRC were "really
OL,11,Fangry".
OL,13,FDame Pat, 82, became a CBE in 2000 and
OL,14,Fis being given her damehood, one of
OL,15,Fthe highest honours in the United
OL,16,FKingdom, for services to literature.
OL,18,FThe Booker Prize winner has published
OL,19,F16 novels, diving into anti-war themes
OL,20,Fincluding trauma and memory.
