OL,6,FDescribing the moment she received the
OL,7,Fnews of her damehood, she said: "I
OL,8,Fpicked up the envelope from the carpet
OL,9,Fand the first thing I noticed, what
OL,10,Fbeautiful quality paper it was, and I
OL,11,Fthought, this is either the income tax
OL,12,Fgetting really angry, or it's
OL,13,Fsomething from the Palace or the
OL,14,FCabinet Office.
OL,16,F"Nobody else does that kind of quality
OL,17,Fof paper. I still sort of had to read
OL,18,Fthe first paragraph several times
OL,19,Fbefore it sank in."
