OL,6,FThe author is known for exploring the
OL,7,Feffects of war in her novels,
OL,8,Fattributing her grandfather and
OL,9,Fstepfather as inspiration for some of
OL,10,Fher most popular books.
OL,12,FShe said: "I was very much a war baby.
OL,13,FMy Victory in Europe Day was my second
OL,14,Fbirthday, and I thought the street
OL,15,Fparties were for me, as any two year
OL,16,Fold would.
OL,18,F"I think in my family, there were
OL,19,Fpeople who bore the very visible
OL,20,Fmental and physical injuries of war.
