OL,6,FShe began writing the Regeneration
OL,7,Ftrilogy in 1991 with the first book
OL,8,Ffollowing English Lieutenant Billy
OL,9,FPrior as he is being treated for
OL,10,Fshellshock.
OL,12,FThe book was adapted into a film in
OL,13,F1997 which starred The Two Popes actor
OL,14,FJonathan Pryce and Maurice's James
OL,15,FWilby.
OL,17,FIn 1993, Dame Pat published the second
OL,18,Fbook in the trilogy, The Eye In The
OL,19,FDoor, which follows William Rivers,
OL,20,Fthe psychiatrist treating Prior at
OL,21,FCraiglockhart Hospital in Edinburgh.
