OL,6,FMore recently, the novelist was
OL,7,Fshortlisted for The Women's Prize For
OL,8,FFiction in 2019 for her book, The
OL,9,FSilence Of The Girls, part of The
OL,10,FWoman Of Troy trilogy, which recounts
OL,11,Fthe lives of women living through the
OL,12,FTrojan War.
OL,14,FIt is followed by The Women Of Troy
OL,15,F(2021) and The Voyage Home (2024), and
OL,16,Fsees the author shift her storytelling
OL,17,Fboth in its genre, from historical
OL,18,Ffiction to myth, and characters,
OL,19,Fwriting from the perspective of women
OL,20,Finstead of men.
